Septenber 30, 1985

Ret Sippl.No.1824-Dr. Crabtree
Appl.No.1828-Dr. Taketo
Appl.No.1832-Dr, Saffer

George Khoury, M.D.
Laboratory of Molecular Virology
National Cencer Institute
Building 41, Room A109

Bethesda, MD 20205

Dear Dr. Khoury:
You have already been informed of our gratitude
for the cogent evaluations you provided of the above cited
applications.
As a token of our appreciation, wo take pleasure
in enclosing an honovariun of $300,

Cordially,

 

HEG/lp
Encl.

50185221
